<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Bitwise - Your Laptop Experts</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #060318;
            --hover-color: #565564;
            --secondary-color: #16a34a;
            --text-color: #1f2937;
            --light-bg: #f9fafb;
            --shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            --border-radius: 12px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: var(--text-color);
            background: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .containerr {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto 51px auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .about-header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background: var(--light-bg);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .about-header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .about-header p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .about-section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .about-section h2 {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .about-section p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .team-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .team-member {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: var(--light-bg);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .team-member img {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .team-member h3 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .team-member p {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--hover-color);
        }

        .contact-info {
            background: var(--light-bg);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .contact-info a {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .contact-info a:hover {
            color: var(--hover-color);
        }
    </style>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/user/header.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/user/footer.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/header') %>

    <div class="containerr">
        <section class="about-header">
            <h1>About Bitwise</h1>
            <p>Bitwise is your premier destination for high-performance laptops, offering a curated selection of the latest models to power your work, gaming, and creativity.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Story</h2>
            <p>Founded in 2020, Bitwise emerged from a passion for technology and a commitment to providing top-tier laptops to enthusiasts, professionals, and students alike. We saw a gap in the market for a retailer that not only sells cutting-edge hardware but also understands the needs of its customers. From our humble beginnings, we’ve grown into a trusted name in the laptop e-commerce space, serving thousands of satisfied customers worldwide.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>At Bitwise, our mission is simple: to empower you with the best tools for success. Whether you’re coding the next big app, dominating in your favorite game, or creating stunning digital art, we provide laptops that deliver performance, reliability, and value. We’re dedicated to exceptional customer service, expert curation, and ensuring every purchase meets your expectations.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <h2>Meet the Team</h2>
            <div class="team-grid">
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/team/shafeeh.jpeg" alt="John Doe">
                    <h3>Shafeeh</h3>
                    <p>Founder & CEO</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/team/jane-smith.jpg" alt="Jane Smith">
                    <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                    <p>Head of Product</p>
                </div>
                <div class="team-member">
                    <img src="/images/team/mike-johnson.jpg" alt="Mike Johnson">
                    <h3>Mike Johnson</h3>
                    <p>Customer Support Lead</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="contact-info">
            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>
            <p>Have questions? Reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@bitwise-laptops.com">support@bitwise-laptops.com</a> or call us at <a href="tel:+1234567890">+1 (234) 567-890</a>.</p>
            <p>Follow us on social media for the latest updates and offers!</p>
            <div class="social-icons mt-3">
                <a href="#" class="mx-2"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="mx-2"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="mx-2"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="mx-2"><i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <%- include('./partials/footer') %>
    

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>